				<tr>
					<td>3</td>
					<td>Larry</td>
					<td>the Bird</td>
					<td>lbird</td>
				</tr>
			</tbody>
		</table>
	</div>
	<pre class="prettyprint">
&lt;table class="datatable condensed">...&lt;/table>
</pre>

	<h3>Grouping</h3>
	<p>To add a grouping effect to the table add a <code>&lt;th></code> in the tbody.</p>

	<h3>No Data Display</h3>
	<p>
		For empty data tables a row in the tbody can have the <code>.datatable-empty</code> class applied to the <code>tr</code> tag.
	</p>

